---------What do we know? -------
52 cards
	red hearts ace, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, Jack, Queen, King
	spades ace, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, Jack, Queen, King
	red diamonds ace, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, Jack, Queen, King
	clubs ace, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, Jack, Queen, King

face up / down
a couple of piles
the piles will all use inheritance from a pile class


